&lt;li&gt;Improve push and pull notification reliability (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/880"&gt;880&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Significant bug fixes&lt;/h3&gt;
