&lt;li&gt;Tolerate missing status fields on veganism.social (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/911"&gt;911&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Render hashtags, mentions, and initial paras correctly in RTL (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/906"&gt;906&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Search filters use correct colours in dark and black mode (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/881"&gt;881&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Translations&lt;/h3&gt;
