&lt;li&gt;Add option to download media to per-sender directories (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/954"&gt;954&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
